<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="crash-n">crash <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kræʃ/    美 /kræʃ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[常用单数] 哗啦声；撞击声；爆裂声：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>At that moment, we hear a huge crash and then silence.
就在那时，我们听到哗啦一声，随后一片寂静。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The tall chimney fell with a great crash.
高高的烟囱轰然倒塌。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>碰撞 (事件)；(飞机) 坠毁：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All the passengers were killed in the <strong>plane crash</strong>.
这次飞机失事，所有乘客无一幸免。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>暴跌；(计算机等的) 崩溃：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>tips for fixing computer system crashes
应对计算机系统崩溃的窍门</p></div></div>